OL,3,CCompany responds to flood fears caused
OL,4,Cby fence
OL,6,FA company has responded to the
OL,7,Fcomplaints of residents who claim a
OL,8,Ffence installed by the firm has caused
OL,9,Fflooding near their homes in Wigton.
OL,11,FThree years ago, CCL Secure installed
OL,12,Fa fence alongside Black Beck, behind
OL,13,Fthe street of Burnside, on what locals
OL,14,Fdescribed as a flood plain for the
OL,15,Fstream.
OL,17,FAfter the beck's water level rose
OL,18,Fsignificantly and spilled onto the
OL,19,Fstreet last week, threatening homes,
OL,20,Fresidents renewed their calls for the
OL,21,Ffence to be reviewed.
