OL,3,CCompany responds to flood fears caused
OL,4,Cby fence
OL,6,FThey say leaves, twigs and debris have
OL,7,Fbuilt up along the boundary and now
OL,8,Fforce water to go into their back
OL,9,Fgardens and onto their road.
OL,11,FLocal Katey Sinclair said: "The water
OL,12,Fhas nowhere to go... it's created
OL,13,Fnature's own dam, a barrier for the
OL,14,Fwater. The only place it can go is
OL,15,F(our road)."
OL,17,FJames Lightfoot has lived on Burnside
OL,18,Ffor 67 years. He said: "I've never
OL,19,Fknown (the water level) so high.
