OL,3,CCompany responds to flood fears caused
OL,4,Cby fence
OL,6,F"With the fence so close to the beck,
OL,7,Fall the debris has run up and covered
OL,8,Fit, so no water can get through."
OL,10,FPatrick Swift, the General Manager of
OL,11,FCCL Secure has now responded to these
OL,12,Fcomplaints.
OL,14,FHe said: "This fence falls into the
OL,15,Fcategory of a 'permitted development'.
OL,16,FThe Local Council carried out site
OL,17,Fvisits and an assessment, this
OL,18,Fincluded a topographic survey in
OL,19,FSeptember 2023 which confirmed that
OL,20,Fthe flood storage area would work as
OL,21,Fintended.
