OL,3,CCompany responds to flood fears caused
OL,4,Cby fence
OL,6,F"We will continue to work closely with
OL,7,Fthe Lead Local Flood Authority to
OL,8,Fensure best practices are followed.
OL,10,F"We remain concerned about the
OL,11,Fpotential impact these events have had
OL,12,Fon local residents and our employees.
OL,14,F"We are committed to ongoing dialogue
OL,15,Fand cooperation with the Local
OL,16,FAuthorities to address any issues that
OL,17,Fmay be identified."
OL,19,FThe local council has been contacted
OL,20,Ffor a comment.
